  <summary date="2022-05-31T12:42:19Z" status="Introduced in House">Federal Death Penalty Abolition Act of 2019

This bill abolishes the federal and military death penalty. It also commutes existing federal and military death penalty sentences to life imprisonment without the possibility of parole.</summary>
